> user
Add a side panel that displays a list of code blocks in the current open convo file. Each item
in the list should have the same options as the code-lens items displayed for the blocks.

Items should be grouped together by containing message.

At the top of the of each group include a button for applying all code blocks

use the `parseConvoCode` function to parse with options.enableCodeBlocks set to true
the source code of content of the file and extract code blocks

``` ts
interface ConvoParsingResult{
    result?: ConvoMessage[];
    error?: CodeParsingError;
    endIndex: number;
}
const parseConvoCode=(code:string,options:{enableCodeBlocks?:boolean}):ConvoParsingResult;
```

